org.smartclean.globalUtility.requestUtil.deviceManagement

Class DeviceMgmtMainRequestObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.smartclean.globalUtility.requestUtil.deviceManagement.DeviceMgmtMainRequestObject

  • public class DeviceMgmtMainRequestObject
extends Object
    Main requestObject wrapper class with all the required fields for making api calls to the endpoints hosted under device management module. Class contains static methods to return instances of itself with mandatory variables populated. Property variables have getter functions annotated with JsonProperty names to facilitate deterministic marshalling/unmarshalling of Object and its JSON format.
